_xResult.title: Fierce and Fly Harem Jumpsuit
_xResult.shortdesc: Custom made jumpsuit with drop crotch in fall colors
_xResult.longdesc:
Ok we see you looking skeptical about this, but we can say that everyone who tries it on falls in love. It's comfortable, modern and elegant - and is definitely a unique look! The one-piece jumper is made in stretchy soft fabric, and the neckline can be worn bateau-style or pulled down for off-shoulder look. The colors are neutral olives, rich browns with deep red accent. Suitable for hijab and abaya style dressing as well. The effect is like a long tunic dress with leggings but all one gorgeous pattern from head to toe.

 

Have fun with EUG's custom made designer clothing! For custom made requests regarding sizing, let the designer know using the button below.
